                <h1>Make Your PowerPoint Background Transparent Effortlessly</h1>
                <p>To make a background transparent in PowerPoint, first, select the image or shape you want to edit. Go to the "Format" tab, click on "Color," and then choose "Set Transparent Color." Click on the color you want to remove to make it transparent. Adjust as needed to enhance your presentation's visual appeal.</p>
